com.tibbo.aggregate.common.datatable

Class SimpleDataTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tibbo.aggregate.common.datatable.AbstractDataTable
      • com.tibbo.aggregate.common.datatable.SimpleDataTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataTable, AttributedObject, PublicCloneable, StringEncodable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<DataTable>, java.lang.Iterable<DataRecord>

    public class SimpleDataTable
extends AbstractDataTable
implements java.lang.Comparable<DataTable>, java.lang.Cloneable
    DataTable is a tabular structure that consist of TableFormat describing table fields and other options and a number of DataRecord objects representing individual records.
